{"title":"Heart Health Supplements","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"deep-sea-fish-oil-capsules-omega-3-2500-mg-lemon","title":"Deep Sea Fish Oil Capsules - 2500 mg Omega 3 (Lemon Flavored)","description":"\u003ch2\u003eNeuherbs Deep Sea Fish Oil – Omega-3 Capsules for Daily Wellness\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp align=\"justify\"\u003eLooking for the best fish oil capsules in India? neuherbs \u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\"\u003edeep sea fish oil\u003c\/span\u003e offers a triple-strength formula designed to support your overall health. These omega-3 fish oil capsules are lemon-flavoured to eliminate fishy burps, making them the perfect fish oil supplement for men and women alike.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eWhy Choose Neuherbs Fish Oil Capsules?\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp align=\"justify\"\u003eNeuherbs brings you premium-quality fish oil capsules sourced from small deep-sea fish like sardines and anchovies. Rich in EPA and DHA, these omega-3 fish oil capsules deliver 2500 mg of pure fish oil per serving and are added with Vitamins E and D3.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHeart Health:\u003c\/strong\u003e Promotes healthy cholesterol level and supports cardiac function.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eBrain Function:\u003c\/strong\u003e Improves memory, focus, \u0026amp; helps manage stress.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSkin \u0026amp; Hair:\u003c\/strong\u003e Among the best fish oil capsules for hair growth and glowing skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eWeight Management:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ideal fish oil capsules for weight loss and metabolism support.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eJoint \u0026amp; Bone Strength:\u003c\/strong\u003e Helps reduce inflammation and aids in muscle recovery.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eProduct Features\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTriple-Strength Omega-3 Fish Oil Capsuless (2500 mg per serving, 2 capsules)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e1486 mg of Omega-3s: 892 mg EPA + 594 mg DHA\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLemon-flavoured softgels – no fishy burps and aftertaste\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFortified with Vitamin D3 and E\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAvailable size includes fish oil 60 capsules and fish oil 200 capsules\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable for all: \u003cstrong\u003efish oil capsules for women\u003c\/strong\u003e improve hormone health and promote healthy pregnancy and fish oil capsules for men aid in post-workout muscle recovery, and brain and vision health.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eBest-Rated Fish Oil Supplements with Quality You Can Trust\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp align=\"justify\"\u003eOur original fish oil capsules undergo 10 quality checks, including molecular distillation and third-party testing to remove heavy metals like mercury, lead, and arsenic. Whether you're buying your first pack or switching to a cleaner brand, this is the best omega-3 fish oil capsule, acclaimed for purity, potency, and effectiveness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eAffordable Fish Oil Capsules Price in India\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp align=\"justify\"\u003eWith neuherbs, you don’t just get the best omega-3 capsules, you get premium quality at a great value. Whether you are comparing fish oil capsules price or omega-3 capsules price, our range delivers unmatched benefits for the price.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eWho Should Use This?\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAnyone looking for omega-3 fish oil capsules for daily heart and brain health\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePeople seeking fish oil capsules for skin ageing or fish oil capsules for hair growth\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFitness enthusiasts using fish oil capsules for weight loss and recovery\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMen and women looking to fill their omega-3 nutritional gap naturally\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Fish Oil - (60 Softgel)","offer_id":40975800926378,"sku":"NDSFO60","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Fish Oil - (120 Softgel)","offer_id":46561937785002,"sku":"NDSFO120","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Fish Oil - (200 Softgel)=Recommended","offer_id":44663434936490,"sku":"NDSFO200","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/deep_sea_fish_oil_1.png?v=1756897940"},{"product_id":"healthy-seeds-mix","title":"Healthy Seeds Mix rich in Vitamin E, healthy fats \u0026 Omega-3 for Heart \u0026 Brain, Immunity \u0026 Bones and Hair \u0026 Skin","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: JA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\"\u003eMade with seeds that carry their own unique benefits, neuherbs Healthy Seeds Mix brings the comprehensive benefits of Pumpkin, Sunflower, Watermelon, Flax and Chia seeds, all packaged in one mix to help you achieve your overall health goals. Being rich in protein, healthy fat, essential vitamins \u0026amp; minerals, neuherbs Healthy Seeds Mix makes a great \u0026amp; healthy option for your untimely hunger cravings. This 5-in-One mix can be enjoyed anytime of the day whether for breakfast with oatmeal \u0026amp; juices or as a late-night munching snack. neuherbs Healthy Seeds Mix can be your wellness companion. Keep it while travelling, going to the office or hiking, it gives you a boost of energy, supports a healthy gut, immunity, heart, brain \u0026amp; bones. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Starter Pack - (200 GM)","offer_id":42510508687530,"sku":"NHSM200","price":179.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard10_40377185-7ff9-4ce0-b8a1-988ba2a92bd9.jpg?v=1718158877"},{"product_id":"omega-seeds-mix","title":"Omega Seeds Mix with richness of Flax, Pumpkin, Watermelon \u0026 Sunflower seeds with omega-3, dietary fiber, protein and essential nutrients helpful for Weight Loss, Heart \u0026 Good Skin","description":"\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\" class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: JA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\"\u003eneuherbs brings to you the highly nutritious Omega-Seeds Mix to help you get the goodness of plant-based or veg Omega- 3 in an easy-to-use snacking pack. This 4-in-1 mix of seeds contains the richness of Flax, Pumpkin, Watermelon \u0026amp; Sunflower seeds to provide various essential nutrients these seeds possess. One of the most vital among them is Omega-3, required by the human body in daily life, but it is difficult for vegetarians to get enough omega-3. This is where neuherbs Omega-Seeds Mix plays an essential role by being a helping hand to meet daily omega-3 requirements, along with the goodness of dietary fiber \u0026amp; protein. So, incorporate these Omega-Seeds Mix into delicious recipes like oatmeal, smoothies, shakes, juices, cakes, and Ladoo's for a healthier tomorrow.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Starter Pack - (200 GM)","offer_id":43374038581418,"sku":"NOSM200","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/omega_seeds_mix_1_d4e5f202-97fe-4df4-89fe-f795e1108878.jpg?v=1748865017"},{"product_id":"mini-deep-sea-fish-oil-1000-mg","title":"Mini Deep Sea Fish Oil 1000 mg (Lemon Flavour)","description":"\u003cp\u003eAre you looking for fish oil small capsules that are easy to swallow? neuherbs’ Mini Deep Sea Fish Oil Capsules solves your problem. Introducing the most potent source of Omega-3 fatty acids in a remarkably compact form. While regular \u003cstrong\u003efish oil capsules\u003c\/strong\u003e can be large and difficult to swallow, these omega 3 mini capsules offer a convenient and effective alternative.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThese small size \u003cstrong\u003eomega 3 capsules\u003c\/strong\u003e are 50% smaller than regular fish oil capsules, yet they deliver double the strength, providing 360mg of EPA and 240mg of DHA per softgel. Each mini fish oil pill also contains Vitamin E (100% RDA) and Vitamin D3 (100% RDA) to improve bone and skin health.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn addition, forget about the unpleasant fishy taste – these mini fish oil capsules are infused with a refreshing lemon flavour to eliminate fishy aftertaste and burps.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eMini Deep Sea Fish Oil Capsules Benefits\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs the only brand offering smallest fish oil capsules in India in natural lemon flavour, neuherbs scientifically researched product delivers a range of health benefits:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImproves Heart Health: Omega-3 fatty acids, especially EPA, help maintain healthy cholesterol levels and blood pressure.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnhances Brain Function: DHA are crucial for cognitive function, memory, and focus.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReduces Inflammation: Omega-3s possess anti-inflammatory properties that may help alleviate joint pain and muscle soreness.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eVitamins D and E: Vitamin E improves absorption of Omega-3s, while Vitamin D ensures healthy bones and cartilage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eneuherbs Quality Assurance\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs is committed to delivering the highest quality omega 3 fish oil mini softgels in India. We test the fish for heavy metal toxicity, including mercury, cobalt, copper, and cadmium, through a process called molecular distillation that offers 100% accurate results. In addition, each batch undergoes rigorous ten-step testing for purity, potency, and freshness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eRecommended Dosage and Packaging\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs \u003cstrong\u003eomega 3 fish oil\u003c\/strong\u003e mini softgels are available in packs of 120 capsules. For best results, take one small fish oil pill twice daily with a meal.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eConsult an expert for free to learn more about your heart health and the benefits of Omega-3 fish oils. Add neuherbs’ Mini Deep Sea Fish Oil Capsules to your everyday routine and experience the numerous benefits of concentrated Omega-3s.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Mini Fish Oil - (120 Softgel)","offer_id":44930057732266,"sku":"NMDSFO120","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Mini Fish Oil - (60 Softgel)","offer_id":47466409525418,"sku":"NMDSFO60","price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Mini Fish Oil - (200 Softgel)","offer_id":44930057765034,"sku":"NMDSFO200","price":999.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Mini_deep_sea_fish_oil_120.webp?v=1772186300"},{"product_id":"omega-flaxseed-oil","title":"Flaxseed Oil Capsules 1000mg With 821mg Omega 3-6-9, Additional Vitamin D3 \u0026 E To Support Heart, Joint \u0026 Skin For Women \u0026 Men","description":"\u003cp\u003eAre you a vegetarian? Wondering how to incorporate\u003cstrong\u003e Omege-3s\u003c\/strong\u003e into your daily diet? neuherbs has made it easy for you. Introducing neuherbs’ Flaxseed Oil Capsules 1000mg - your plant-based Omega-3-6-9 powerhouse.  The supplement is a natural and potent source of Omega-3 fatty acids derived from flaxseeds. While fish oil is a popular choice, flaxseed oil provides a vegetarian and vegan-friendly option, rich in alpha-linolenic acid (ALA), a precursor to EPA and DHA.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs flaxseed oil capsules deliver a 500mg concentrated dose of ALA, supporting overall health and well-being. It also contains 134 mg of Omega-6 (Linoleic acid) and 187mg of Omega-9 (Oleic acid).\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn addition, the \u003cstrong\u003eOmega-3 flaxseed oil supplements\u003c\/strong\u003e are fortified with Vitamin D and Vitamin E to enhance bone and skin health.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eFlaxseed Oil Capsules 1000mg Benefits\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs one of the best flaxseed oil capsules in India, neuherbs scientifically-researched product offers a range of health benefits:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSupports Heart Health: Flaxseed Omega-3 fatty acids contribute to cardiovascular wellness by helping maintain healthy cholesterol levels and blood pressure.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePromotes Brain Function: ALA is converted into EPA and DHA, which are crucial for cognitive function, memory, and focus.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReduces Inflammation: Omega-3s possess anti-inflammatory properties that may help alleviate joint pain, muscle soreness, and other inflammatory conditions.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProtects Bone Health: neuherbs flaxseed oil capsules contain plant-based Vitamin D3, which supports bone health and improves signs of deficiency, such as back pain and buckling joints.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSupports Healthy Skin and Hair: ALA contributes to skin hydration and elasticity, promoting a healthy complexion and lustrous hair. The addition of Vitamin E, which is a potent antioxidant, further intensifies the results.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFlaxseed oil benefits for females: Omega-3 fatty acids, DHA in particular, help in foetal brain development, improving cognitive power and eye health in the womb. Vegetarian moms can also consume neuherbs Omega 3 flaxseed oil tablets to reduce the risks of preterm delivery.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eneuherbs Quality Assurance\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs is committed to delivering the highest quality \u003cstrong\u003eomega-3 flaxseed oil capsules\u003c\/strong\u003e in India. Our flaxseeds are carefully selected from top organic farmers and cold-pressed to preserve their natural goodness. Each batch undergoes ten-step rigorous testing for purity, potency, and freshness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFurthermore, the capsules do not contain additives, artificial colours, trans fats, or preservatives.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eRecommended Dosage and Packaging\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs omega 3 flaxseed oil tablets are available in packs of 60 capsules. For best results, take one softgel twice daily with a meal for at least three months. Since it is a natural product, it is recommended to store it in a cool, dry, and dark place to avoid rancidification.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTo know more about your heart health and the benefits of Omgea-3 flaxseed oils, consult an expert for free.  Add neuherbs Flaxseed Oil Capsules 1000mg to your everyday meals and experience the numerous benefits of plant-based omega-3s.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Smart Pack - 60 Capsules","offer_id":44650834428074,"sku":"NOFSO60","price":499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Value Pack - 120 Capsules","offer_id":46122553442474,"sku":"NOFSO60P2","price":998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Flaxseed_oil_capsule_1.webp?v=1772175772"},{"product_id":"deep-sea-cod-liver-oil-capsules-for-heart-brain","title":"Deep Sea Cod Liver Oil Capsules for Heart \u0026 Brain","description":"\u003cp\u003eAre you looking for a natural alternative to fish oil supplements to boost your heart and brain health? \u003cstrong\u003eCod liver oil capsules\u003c\/strong\u003e are an excellent choice. neuherbs Deep Sea Cod Liver Oil Capsules 600 mg offer a potent blend of Omega-3 fatty acids (180mg), Vitamin D3, and Vitamin E in one convenient soft gel. Obtained from the depths of the Atlantic and Pacific oceans, our cod liver oil is a rich source of essential nutrients that support overall well-being.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCod fish is a time-tested source of Omega-3s, known for their numerous health benefits. These fish get their Omega-3s by absorbing the microalgae after consuming phytoplanktons. Each capsule contains high levels of EPA and DHA, vital for maintaining a healthy heart and sharp mind. Cod liver oil also contains vitamins A and D and remarkable anti-inflammatory properties. So, with neuherbs, you not only get the benefits of Omega-3 fatty acids, but also 100% RDA of Vitamin A, D, and E.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhat’s more? Our lemon-flavoured capsules eliminate the unpleasant aftertaste and fishy burps commonly associated with cod liver oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eCod Liver Oil Capsules Benefits\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs Deep Sea Cod Liver Oil Capsules offer a range of health benefits:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eKeeps Your Heart Healthy: Omega-3 fatty acids help maintain healthy cholesterol levels and blood pressure, promoting cardiovascular wellness.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImproves Your Brain Function: DHA is crucial for cognitive function, memory, and focus, supporting a sharp and healthy mind.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBoosts Your Immunity: Vitamin D3 and anti-inflammatory drugs help modulate the immune system and keep infections at bay.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMaintains Healthy Bones: Vitamin D3 is essential for calcium absorption and bone health, ensuring you have stronger bones, cartilage, and muscles.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOffers Antioxidant Support: Vitamin E acts as a powerful antioxidant, protecting cells from oxidative damage. This helps improve gut, skin, and hair health.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNourishes Skin: The anti-inflammatory properties and antioxidants together help boost skin cell production, protect them from stress and inflammation, and reduce the signs of ageing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eCod Liver Oil Benefits for Female\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOmega-3 fatty acids, particularly DHA, are essential during pregnancy for fetal brain development. It can potentially improve your unborn baby’s brain function and retina development. By taking the best cod liver oil for adults, you can also reduce the risks of preterm delivery.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eneuherbs Quality Check\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs delivers high-quality health supplements with scientifically tested formulations. Our Deep Sea Cod Liver Oil undergoes molecular distillation and third-party testing for purity, efficiency, and safety. Free from preservatives, artificial colours, flavours, and gluten, they are the best cod liver oil capsules in India.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eDosage and Packaging\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs \u003cstrong\u003eDeep Sea Cod Liver Oil Capsules Omega 3\u003c\/strong\u003e are available in bottles of 100 capsules. For best results, take one capsule twice daily with a meal.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eConsult with a healthcare professional to learn more about your specific health needs and the benefits of Omega-3 fatty acids, Vitamin D3, and Vitamin E.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Deep Sea Cod Liver - (100 softgel)","offer_id":46151832600746,"sku":"NDSCLO100","price":299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Deep_sea_cod_liver_oil_1.webp?v=1767179761"}],"url":"https:\/\/neuherbs.com\/collections\/heart-health-supplements.oembed","provider":"Neuherbs","version":"1.0","type":"link"}